id anything with it.\n\n[Speaker E] I talked to somebody about it and.\n\n[Speaker C] They took my information. This was pretty late at night. I'm thinking I left their house at like midnight 1am but I could be wrong. But when I was coming back like a 20 mile ride back home, I called the local police department to see if anybody else had reported anything. They said no, of course they probably thought I was crazy. And you know, this was before the government confirmed they have sightings that they can't explain, but I'm sure they don't have any recording of me calling. I just know it's probably the summer of 2008, but it was definitely something that I can't explain and I tried to be very logical. So I'm going to call it a UAP ufo. I think MUFON did too. And stuff does happen over eastern Iowa, along the Mississippi and Dubuque County. I appreciate your podcast. It's something I listen to very often and I hope to maybe call back someday with some other stories.	1309.5	1512.2	ufo	Northern Dubuque County, Iowa	\N	t	709	full	[-0.02507873,0.03178583,-0.046366487,-0.024058083,-0.008821297,-0.027703248,-0.009914846,0.045200035,0.024349697,0.005467746,-0.049574234,0.023183243,-0.05832263,0.011445816,-0.06619618,0.034264542,0.03280648,-0.023183243,0.031202607,-0.01800711,0.024495503,0.038492933,0.04082584,0.005467746,-0.051323917,-0.020558726,-0.04286713,0.04286713,0.01064388,0.001849921,-0.014799367,-0.014289044,-0.031640027,-0.00128492,-0.0466581,-0.023912277,-0.04724133,0.005905166,-0.012539365,0.016767755,0.065904565,-0.00215976,0.010498073,-0.021579374,-0.005795811,-0.02755744,-0.004064358,0.028723894,0.003991455,0.011883236,-0.03280648,0.001731453,0.002214437,0.041409064,-0.019246466,-0.008165168,0.01910066,0.03353551,-0.011883236,0.037618097,0.001950163,-0.026245182,0.006998715,0.021141954,-0.047824554,-0.004538229,0.007654845,-0.029307121,-0.014507754,-0.020996146,0.021433566,-0.026974216,0.00092496,-0.019683886,0.04549165,0.03616003,0.007071618,0.006962264,-0.01232