ist told me. So anyone that's ever had morphine, it makes you feel literal warmth and euphoria just, like all over your body. And that's what I felt when this thing smiled at me with its mouth full of sharp teeth. And then as I stared at this thing for maybe five to 10 seconds, it just slowly faded out. I think I just went back to sleep and I just thought, wow, that was really interesting. And I thought, I'll tell my girlfriend about that tomorrow. She wasn't even in bed with me at the time. I was by myself. Anyway, I never forgot about it. Probably happened like maybe 15 years ago now. And I thought I'd pass it along because I just think it's a different twist on the whole sleep paralysis thing because I wasn't paralyzed. In fact, I felt amazing. Anyway, I love the show. Have a good one.	3666.3	3877.1	sleep_paralysis	Salt Lake City, Utah	\N	t	677	full	[0.003879139,-0.01852723,0.001389542,-0.001066281,0.047862012,-0.009649599,0.016983295,0.04168627,0.024548579,-0.06484531,-0.06638925,-0.014590194,-0.043230202,-0.009881189,-0.026092516,-0.014667391,-0.020843135,0.03535613,-0.014744588,-0.021615101,0.007102105,0.01760087,0.060522288,0.05249382,-0.03597371,0.025474943,-0.048479587,0.035047345,0.007179302,0.02192389,0.039524756,0.01397262,0.007719679,-0.022541465,-0.051567458,0.025474943,0.003338761,-0.006909113,-0.023159038,-0.02964357,0.010189977,0.04261263,0.011502323,0.004844099,0.014744588,-0.018450035,-0.004882697,0.053420182,0.011888307,-0.001138653,-0.04292142,-0.03828961,0.006330137,0.056199264,-0.02022556,0.053420182,0.039524756,0.024239793,-0.003242265,0.022078283,-0.006870515,-0.002286955,-0.04353899,-0.027636452,-0.016906098,0.03828961,0.005133587,-0.011347929,0.03566492,0.045391716,0.024548579,-0.041068695,-0.024085399,0.054346543,0.015516555,0.044465356,0.007681081,-0.002373802,-0.008260056,-0.00409143,-0.031187506,-0.07194742,0.016520113,-0.006909113,0.018372836,0.029180389,-0.01806405,-0.004940595,0.054964118,0.005480973,-0.020071167,0.002972077,0.02393