lack mass seeping down into my room, coming from above. And above his room and that he lived in the basement, was the living room. So he was seeing whatever I was seeing from below. Until very recently, I didn't know this, but we talked about it again. My mom passed about 11 years ago. And he told me when he saw that seeping down, he went upstairs and he went to the living room and looked same area that I was looking at. He told me that he not only saw darkness mass, but he could see like a sparkling, like a stardust swirling within that dark mass. He said that the feeling he got from wasn't good. He always felt like it could have been maybe some kind of opening of some kind of portal or something, but just mind boggling because I saw it and he saw it. Anyways. Love your show. Thank you.	184	418.5	ghost	Ontario, Canada	\N	t	696	full	[0.008763227,0.01811558,0.024006825,-0.031812724,-0.004400024,-0.04506803,0.037409406,0.023859542,0.005118019,-0.003995,-0.043006092,-0.000317575,-0.08129918,0.017452814,-0.039765906,-0.022681294,0.015243596,-0.056555953,-0.010088758,-0.036967564,0.023859542,-0.003995,0.038293093,-0.002227627,-0.021503046,-0.006001706,-0.07128406,0.042711526,-0.013108021,0.013476223,-0.012739818,0.034758344,-0.04830821,-0.003829309,-0.018041939,0.051253833,0.01841014,0.016495487,-0.022828575,-0.007658619,0.05331577,0.0335801,0.011929771,-0.013697145,0.044773463,-0.015169957,-0.008726407,0.05478858,0.026068758,-0.022975855,-0.026952446,0.014286269,-0.023564981,0.018483782,-0.007916361,0.042416964,0.012297974,-0.012960739,-0.005670324,0.051548395,0.012960739,-0.025774198,-0.020766638,0.061858073,-0.017673736,0.002135576,-0.02223945,-0.011782491,0.051253833,0.03284369,-0.00096193,-0.018336501,-0.011414288,0.028277976,-0.004897098,0.00070879,-0.027541572,0.030634474,0.034905627,-0.014875393,-0.014801754,-0.01958839,0.03564203,-0.002227627,-0.018483782,-0.013549864,-0.01811558,0.010088758,-0.019735672,0.009241891,0.025774198,-0.013844427,-0.004418434,0.013623