 like normal people. Just hiding her notepad. I looked around to make sure there's no other cars. There's no other cars in the area. You're on a main road and there was cars driving past, but there was no other cars parked on the side or anything where somebody got out or anything like that. So I had no idea where they came from. As I said, when I was running down the driveway, there was no one there. As I jumped on the fence, these five guys in black suits were there. Now, this has all happened within a short period. I jumped back off the fence. I've ran probably maybe 5 meters, and I've turned back to have a look because I was going to go and go get my mum. As I've turned back to have a look, those five men in black suits were gone. I've always called them Men in Black, but if it's not the real Men in black, the way that they've been described, or anything like that, I've always wondered and thought, what if they're angelic creatures or angels writing down notes to collect my dog's soul when he passed away? It's baffled me for years. Can't think of anything that would describe what I actually saw that day. But yeah, Loving the podcast. Have a good one.	3860.7	4076.5	other	Australia	\N	t	796	full	[-0.02560107,-0.026787873,0.00915535,-0.038486376,-0.00108084,-0.03729957,0.02950057,0.030348288,0.004704832,0.04408131,-0.006654582,0.0222102,-0.006188338,-0.005298235,-0.019412732,-0.022549286,0.012546219,-0.041877244,-0.000468894,-0.000649034,0.025940157,0.0036028,-0.010681241,0.033060983,-0.023905635,-0.013309165,0.029839657,0.024414264,-0.018734558,0.005976409,0.03729957,-0.04543766,-0.02950057,-0.024583807,-0.00801093,-0.003814729,-0.029670114,-0.011868046,-0.011698502,-0.014835057,0.0888408,0.02271883,-0.013224394,-0.052897576,-0.024075177,0.00176961,-0.028144222,0.07358188,-0.004132623,-0.028822398,-0.03102646,-0.000709963,0.014495971,0.018734558,-0.019158415,0.033908702,0.030178744,0.027635591,0.04645492,0.026957417,-0.000249017,0.00555255,-0.05323666,0.037808202,