stand now that I'm 33 that there's some biology involved with what you wake up, the crust on your eyes. I get it. But even still, now, as an adult, I still stand by what I saw that night, what I experienced, what I felt. I don't know what it was, but to this day I just call it the Sandman. I've never told anyone about this ever, other than my parents. Anyways, I appreciate your hard work for us, Derek. Peace.\n\n[Speaker B] Well folks, what do you think? Weird enough for you? Thank you JW for creeping us out.	4000.4	4189.2	sleep_paralysis	Alabama	\N	t	621	full	[-0.016432479,-0.005953292,0.013159909,-0.010374743,0.01302065,-0.057374418,0.014622121,0.038713805,0.045955237,-0.011976213,-0.05988107,-0.017128771,-0.02200281,0.039549354,-0.0069281,0.00410812,-0.002132393,0.015457671,0.022977619,-0.020888744,0.007415504,0.034118284,0.025066493,0.032029405,-0.01796432,-0.032307927,-0.003046275,0.050411504,-0.006301438,0.038713805,0.002297762,-0.009678451,-0.02047097,-0.023256136,-0.039549354,0.004839226,0.023395395,-0.004804411,0.006649584,0.001053141,0.03927084,0.044562656,0.024230944,-0.008390312,0.033839766,-0.04010639,-0.01392583,0.050968535,-0.006266623,-0.010374743,-0.034536056,0.015875446,0.004978484,0.011488809,-0.014970267,0.019356903,0.077984646,-0.003411828,-0.00131425,0.023952426,0.033143476,0.02214207,-0.017128771,0.027712401,0.000992215,-0.010862147,-0.007171802,-0.03523235,0.017825061,0.05486777,0.010235485,-0.031611633,-0.023116877,0.03759974,-0.017546546,-0.006231809,-0.013786571,0.03676419,-0.00308109,-0.006893286,-0.002454428,-0.016710997,0.05236112,-0.022420585,0.001157585,0.006997729,-0.004560709,-0.020610228,0.03537161,0.001079252,0.021028003,0.039549354,0.02047097,0.037878256,-0.024787977,0.022281328,-0.0654514,0.012324359,0.034536056,-0.017059142,0.0654514,0.038992323,-0.009469564,0.034814574,0.013716943,0.011697697,0.02618056,0.047069304,-0.005744405,-0.000970456,-0.011071035,0.011628068,-0.051247053,-0.012672505,0.04428414,-0.017476916,-0.005953292