helming sensation that while it floated in my window, it was almost trying to decide whether it wanted to take me or not. And eventually, after what felt like an eternity, but probably wasn't any longer than one minute, this thing just sort of floated away and left my window. It was many years before I ever shared this story with anyone, so I thought I'd share it it here. It's been really formative in shaping my views on UFOs or any kind of mysterious stories that people share. So thanks so much and great job on the pod.	458.9	604.6	ufo	Morgan Hill, California	\N	t	594	full	[-0.037689812,-0.002757346,-0.008874636,-0.028340401,0.015923215,-0.025272626,-0.015411919,0.035936795,0.046747055,-0.01957533,-0.036521137,-0.036082882,-0.07158142,-0.018479694,-0.05112959,-0.003926022,0.038566317,-0.028194316,0.027025642,-0.04528621,0.03184643,0.0321386,0.081223,0.021328343,-0.036521137,0.02030575,-0.07245793,0.033891615,-0.00609903,0.023081359,0.03827415,0.022935273,-0.021036174,-0.012709356,-0.038566317,0.008874636,-0.033599447,0.000465644,-0.02571088,0.002081705,0.039442826,0.04236452,0.001798666,0.001981272,0.014754538,-0.011613721,0.000744118,0.028194316,0.001953881,-0.027463896,-0.012709356,0.017603189,-0.030969923,0.07771698,-0.03915066,0.059894662,0.063108526,0.015411919,-0.007961608,0.034768123,-0.017530145,-0.033599447,-0.027902147,0.03184643,-0.05171393,0.018406652,-0.036521137,-0.04470187,0.04762356,0.045578375,0.033161193,-0.03579071,-0.002036053,0.003049515,-0.010883298,0.005332086,-0.02863257,-0.021474428,-0.0321386,-0.013366736,-0.003104297,0.01095634,0.030385586,-0.013658905,0.009203326,0.031116007,0.005332086,-0.012709356,0.014389327,-0.012782398,0.009130284,0.03374553,0.049376577,0.011248509,0.020744005,0.030531669,-0.015338877,-0.033307277,0.01636147,-0.003907762,0.058141645,0.05142176,0.008253776,0.013951073,-0.03345336,0.003487768,0.017822314,0.049668744,-0.02571088,-0.02118226,-0.018479694,0.036813304,-0.034768123,-0.01957533,0.040319335,-0.008180735,-0.0