 or, you know, upstairs? There is an upstairs, like, loft area. Even though I knew there was no way he could have gotten from that part of the restaurant back over to the kitchen without me seeing him. And he said, no, I've been in here. And I said, well, is anyone else supposed to be over there? He's like, no. So we go over. There is no one in the lower part, the other side of the restaurant. There is no one upstairs. And actually, as a matter of fact, as soon as we went upstairs, the hair on the back of his arm stood up and he had goosebumps. And I did see that. So that was something kind of crazy that happened. It reminds me of, like, a mimic, because it sounded just like his whistle enough for me to not take my phone out because I thought he was, you know, in the vicinity right there. So, yeah, thanks so much, Derek. Have a great day.	1854	2040.8	ghost	Westover, Vermont	\N	t	694	full	[-0.005697455,-0.041406855,0.048147507,-0.029048996,0.033863746,-0.033703253,0.001324056,0.046863575,0.010752943,0.000299668,-0.02856752,-0.03225883,-0.041406855,0.04590062,-0.05135734,0.001835624,0.05232029,-0.015246711,-0.045579642,-0.024234245,-0.00974987,0.022147853,0.043011773,-0.014604744,-0.025839161,0.01966023,-0.055209137,0.07446814,-0.046863575,0.054888155,-0.033542763,-0.010752943,-0.025197195,-0.012839335,-0.015166464,-0.010993681,-0.016771382,-0.011555401,0.008064708,-0.034826696,0.07671503,-0.014043022,0.015487447,-0.03145637,0.033542763,-0.029209487,-0.006138807,-0.007021511,0.06901143,-2.2883e-05,-0.012117122,-0.006660405,-0.011956631,0.042369805,-0.01332081,0.003029281,0.011796139,-0.002046269,-0.002728359,0.011876384,0.015005973,0.022629326,-0.021505887,0.026481127,0.004654259,-0.025518179,-0.014765236,0.006780773,0.044295706,0.004955181,0.03498719,0.014845481,-0.054246187,0.047184557,-0.03546866,0.039801937,0.016771382,0.016049169,-0.015567694,-0.035629157,-0.054567173,-0.047826525,0.039480954,-0.015407202,0.034666203,-0.01564794,-0.054246187,-0.005737578,-0.04012